<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.6">
<l>pāleṉkō nāṉku vētap payaṉeṉkō camaya nīti</l>
<l>nūleṉkō nuṭaṅku kēḷvi yicaiyeṉkō vivaṟṟu ṇalla</l>
<l>mēleṉkō viṉaiyiṉ mikka payaṉeṉkō kaṇṇa ṉeṉkō</l>
<l>māleṉkō māya ṉeṉkō vāṉava rāti yaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Will I say “milk”? Will I say “benefit of the Veda”? Will I say “treatise</l>
<l>of dogmatic rules”? Will I say “music of swaying sound”? Will I say “goodness on top</l> 
<l>in these”? Will I say “abundant fruit of karma”? Will I say “Kṛṣṇa”?</l>
<l>Will I say “Māl”? Will I say “trickster”? – to the first of the celestials.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
